4578-9bd0-eccf862d512e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f246bfce-5f29-4bc3-a7b3-73b62e6609df\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>적합한 이유</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5d1686eb-69ee-4733-bd85-d353d3c3998e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-574a30a7-44de-4ff8-8b7b-3b31dae9feda\" style=\"color:#555555;\">작지만 가치가 높은 제품에 묵직하고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-126df8e6-4ba8-4110-ab02-fb9861fadf58\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d4966cbb-a319-42e1-90fd-60ac338ecd7f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고급스러운 느낌을 더해주어,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5bdf824c-d13c-4cc8-90b7-e8c9be871487\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6a50c1b4-3a5a-4199-a40d-8a9088e6a61d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">단순한 포장을 넘어</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0101a16b-3ea6-4c78-b156-1b74fe1b002a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b172c681-8d97-4562-a617-71839025b93b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제품의 가치를 높이는 역할을 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3ccece0f-a70a-42da-993d-3a46294c3501\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-adf716a0-ba7b-4fd6-af3c-ec9e2d7c2770\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6eda878a-8513-4d35-ad5f-8653ce312dbd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8f943b61-01cf-4cec-b722-639d80f64663\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">예시</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-03a0cd2e-bd80-4e3e-a161-04aef1b0467f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a18155e5-7826-4fa7-b430-15eca6d639e8\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">시계, 목걸이, 귀금속 세트,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-42d1f616-3576-4385-b2aa-bce5a65aedad\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5a0bc4d4-13a5-4a7e-8415-e3ae30292b71\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">고급 지갑이나 벨트 등</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f353bbdb-27e3-4e6e-a23a-13194cec917c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224051130388/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-263cd1d5-c03e-4173-a429-d46eca316af7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ca79b56a-a171-4d1d-a1c0-bb73bf7f5e57\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-30c394af-8a02-4397-8d5b-d72e550c7ad7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">요약하자면, 제품의 가격대가 높거나,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ec029e32-756a-4942-a1c5-a0e0d18efb91\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0f433d0a-710c-4d7e-a77b-b67393f6ced4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">선물용으로 포장하여</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b263d82c-179a-4dea-8d7b-30f0c1d391ab\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-71fa2efa-7e62-4220-9fe2-471fcd1dc76f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>특별함</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c6b576f3-83e3-4bdf-92fe-f11933d66845\" style=\"color:#555555;\">과 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-53e41a91-bbb1-401d-809a-aa82ca9dfb83\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>고급스러움</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-58113ddd-8d8d-429e-8899-0d37a39cae10\" style=\"color:#555555;\">을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a6adcf3a-f3c2-44a5-b0a0-3da678536bd4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-22c53b2e-3260-4c96-b70b-c18dd59cca49\" style=\"color:#555555;\">강조하고 싶을 때</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d693e420-b157-4e2f-b480-35e48083d3fd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6eb58749-b4bc-421b-ad23-f1d5825e9935\" style=\"color:#555555;\">3단 싸바리 박스가</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4e2f1e71-ff37-4622-adfd-8b8f3c372918\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1cd55003-7de8-4188-bddf-c06ed0f2b7a9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가장 좋은 선택이 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6d8051ff-2e21-4626-ae2c-3e8bc1cbcd2d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-86f6c06f-99c6-405d-9883-848b157e278a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-927e2011-7ffb-4553-8064-fd69ca22db7a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ff8bc5cd-50ff-439f-92f9-c75c7f00f201\" style=\"color:#36851e;\"><b>3단 싸바리 박스의 특징</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-56f23661-a2da-4b96-8d4c-d775e09e6396\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-41da9473-316b-413b-872d-1242e4e5d8d3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e384065f-b306-4dd2-a993-505f572ef81e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5623f20d-2985-4cf6-83fd-049ba08337f0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">□ 일반적인 종이 박스보다 단단하고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1464dbd4-d9d2-49f6-9333-c5cdd6d71650\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0129bebf-ff68-4d9f-b0b1-38cf4947419f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">내구성이 우수합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2ed5df92-af9b-4e76-bfdf-ef4cd4eb358e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2aab4482-f536-4614-84f4-f09b008ffe1f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b5e415fb-187d-41fb-a757-6a285be0e7d8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c0401025-ecb9-41bc-b616-b2251df46345\" style=\"color:#555555;\">□ 겉감의 재질과 후가공(박, 형압 등)을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-146c7493-1c9f-4bc8-bc64-5bda03125d5f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8cde0448-ea33-4add-b582-5b38685e2905\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다양하게 적용할 수 있어</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bf6ea7e6-821b-4fa2-baf5-2dad8ed3ad78\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-25da5c4d-26bc-4d47-b9c9-80cd9fb55aa7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고급스럽고 세련된 느낌을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f16b182e-65ec-4440-ae99-8557886c8ca2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-57c27897-d207-4fa5-8312-3f18733e2f51\" style=\"color:#555555;\">줄 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7825cb1e-ad5c-4d58-8aab-9cb091e192b5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ab9a2042-d91a-4cf3-bed6-1f7b8d8144cd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2d268f39-edfb-4c4f-94d7-786aae6c2cd1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-bb256588-d7c0-47f9-be44-b9977fc2e24a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">□ 가장 비쌉니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-983f94f1-1fab-4d6e-be66-4d9bfd8cbd56\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b8887592-7cd8-4959-9443-e74bb13fb958\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 가장 고급스럽습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-90aaab6a-e1d4-4987-9c2e-8035f78ada6f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-86a73b58-8aff-43aa-9af7-03bc1645d82c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-16559ffe-a67b-40b8-842c-7269b796e68a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8fddcc99-ae66-494e-9d10-3993c7ef3afd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fc4000f8-c1ac-4435-95da-cf74b6bcb8a1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-67552eb7-399b-468a-96af-4ff4e72fb333\" style=\"color:#36851e;\"><b>3단 싸바리 박스의 구성</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-56707a02-03e7-4c2b-8e1c-efaff987eee7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c67a916b-9633-4935-a2cd-a23eaab15b2e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e28613fe-7223-40cf-8a41-62503d7badc8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a7f2113c-1d43-44d3-a1e9-4b134e729fa0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">일반적인 싸바리 박스 형태인</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-82a5c5a2-bd9c-4ce3-84bc-6585f7cdef67\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2a7476a3-a0f8-47cd-883b-6298c4d616f1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">2단 상하 박스</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-114504c1-2dd6-435d-ab9e-f1714f77744f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-06817ddd-40a1-4b1a-b747-e935a00709cc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(뚜껑과 밑 상자로 구성)와</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragrap